{#
  Partial: Chapter Navigation
  ===========================
  Renders sequential prev/next navigation links at the bottom of documentation pages.
  This snippet checks if the "ChapterNav" feature has calculated navigation data for
  the current file.

  Dependencies:
  - Requires the 'ChapterNav' feature to be active given it relies on
    `features.ChapterNav`.

  Variables:
  - source_file: (string) The relative path of the current content file (e.g. "guide/index.md")
  - features.ChapterNav.pages: (array) Global lookup table for navigation data.
#}

{% if features.ChapterNav.pages[source_file] is defined %}
    {% for menu_num, nav_data in features.ChapterNav.pages[source_file] %}
        {{ nav_data.html|raw }}
    {% endfor %}
{% endif %}

